# Phase 20 — Deployment to Vercel

**Steps:**
1. Push to GitHub: `git init && git add . && git commit -m "JARVIS v1" && git push`
2. Go to [vercel.com](https://vercel.com) → Import repo
3. Add all env variables from `.env.local` in Vercel dashboard
4. Set `NEXTAUTH_URL` = your Vercel URL
5. In Supabase → Auth → URL Config → add your Vercel URL to **Redirect URLs**
6. In Google Cloud Console → OAuth → add Vercel URL to **Authorized redirect URIs**

Your teacher can now open the Vercel URL, click "Sign in with Google", and everything works instantly. [github](https://github.com/supabase-community/ai-writer)

